TechFlag IDP Community Authors
==============================

Primary Author and Copyright Holder
-----------------------------------

TechFlag is the original author, copyright holder, and primary maintainer of
TechFlag IDP Community.

Copyright (C) 2026 TechFlag.

Project Maintainer
------------------

- TechFlag

Original Work
-------------

TechFlag created and maintains the original project architecture, including:

- Backend service architecture and API contracts.
- Document parsing, review, evidence, and extraction workflow design.
- Community/commercial edition capability and guardrail design.
- Vue-based workbench user interface and interaction model.
- Document application, Skill authoring, and runtime workflow concepts.
- Release packaging, public snapshot export, and source attribution tooling.
- Public documentation, user manuals, release notes, and community setup flow.

