this repository are intended to be contributed under the same license as the
project: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 only (`AGPL-3.0-only`).

Contributors retain copyright in their own contributions unless they assign it
by written agreement. By submitting a contribution, the contributor represents
that they have the right to contribute it under the project license.

